## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-102"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService>物件可讓您讀取使用者的角色，透過 Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) 服務。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-102">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService> object enables you to read a user's roles through a Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-103">若要使用的角色服務，您必須啟用 Web 伺服器上的角色服務，並再連接到 Web 服務相容的 WCF 用戶端應用程式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-103">To use the role service, you must enable the role service on a Web server and then connect a WCF-compatible client application to the Web service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-104">如需如何設定角色服務的資訊，請參閱[How to： 啟用 WCF 角色服務](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d021aa39-4cbf-4450-a3c1-d5573ca7ce8c)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-104">For information about how to configure the role service, see [How to: Enable the WCF Role Service](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d021aa39-4cbf-4450-a3c1-d5573ca7ce8c).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-105">使用者必須經過驗證才能讀取使用者的角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-105">The user must be authenticated to read the user's roles.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-106">角色服務的運作方式與任何一種 ASP.NET 驗證。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-106">The role service works with any kind of ASP.NET authentication.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-107">如需如何將記錄中透過 WCF 服務的使用者資訊，請參閱[Windows Communication Foundation 驗證服務概觀](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6e121a28-89e8-4974-88a8-70aaa6a7d52b)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-107">For information about how to log users in through a WCF service, see [Windows Communication Foundation Authentication Service Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6e121a28-89e8-4974-88a8-70aaa6a7d52b).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-108"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService>類別會公開兩種方法，應該只透過 WCF 服務來存取：<xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A>方法和<xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-108">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService> class exposes two methods that should be accessed only through a WCF service: the <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A> method and the <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-109"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A>方法會傳回已登入使用者的所有角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-109">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A> method returns all the roles for the logged-in user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-110"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A>方法會判斷使用者是否在指定的角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-110">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A> method determines whether the user is in a specified role.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-111"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService>物件引發<xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.SelectingProvider>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-111">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService> object raises the <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.SelectingProvider> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-112">您建立的事件處理常式<xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.SelectingProvider>事件，以選取要在執行階段使用角色提供者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-112">You create an event handler for the <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.SelectingProvider> event to select which role provider to use at run time.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e04a-113">如需如何使用 WCF 的角色服務，從主控台應用程式的範例，請參閱[逐步解說： 使用 ASP.NET 應用程式服務](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f3f394f0-20d6-4361-aa8f-4b21bf4933eb)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e04a-113">For an example of how to use the WCF role service from a console application, see [Walkthrough: Using ASP.NET Application Services](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f3f394f0-20d6-4361-aa8f-4b21bf4933eb).</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
